# .geminiignore
# This file defines which files and directories should be ignored by the Gemini CLI.
# Rules here have HIGHER priority than .gitignore.

# 1. Unblock critical AI context files (even if they are in .gitignore)
!.gemini/
!GEMINI.md

# 2. Add any AI-specific ignores here if needed
# (By default, it still respects .gitignore unless configured otherwise,
# but we can explicitly exclude high-volume/low-signal data)
.local/
.reference/
node_modules/
vendor/
storage/logs/
public/build/
public/hot/
public/storage/
*.log
